      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           perform   acc-des-rdc-000      thru acc-des-rdc-999        .
           if        w-cnt-tus-acc-tes    not  = spaces
                     go to acc-tes-reg-999.
       acc-tes-reg-900.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Assestamento status di uscita                   *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        v-key                =    "DO  "
                     move   "S"           to   w-cnt-tus-acc-tes
           else if   v-key                =    "DELT"
                     move   "X"           to   w-cnt-tus-acc-tes
           else if   v-key                =    "EXIT"
