      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       del-rec-yrc-000.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Composizione record                             *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           perform   cmp-rec-yrc-000      thru cmp-rec-yrc-999        .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Delete record                                   *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "DE"                 to   f-ope                  .
           move      "pgm/cdp/fls/ioc/obj/iofyrc"
                                          to   s-pat                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mfiltp"
                                         using s                      .
           call      s-pat               using f
                                               rf-yrc                 .
       del-rec-yrc-999.
